data.description: 4 bedroom 3 bath home with a pool in Castle Ridge subdivision, a beautiful gated community. This well maintained home features an open floor plan with approximately 2797 sqft of living space, high decorative ceilings, large walk in closets, and a spacious office area that can also be used as a second living area. The kitchen has a lot of granite countertop space including an island and a pantry room. The primary bedroom is amazing. Whether you're getting ready for a night out or unwinding from a long day at work, the primary bathroom has it all. Soak in your jetted tub for relaxation, then get ready at ease at the extended sitting area. The large wrap around closet is definitely an area you'll appreciate. We can all agree that the RGV can get very hot often. Walk outside and BBQ under the covered patio or take a dip in your pool. With 8,152 sqft of land, there is much room to entertain your guests. Schedule a showing to see this property to appreciate all of its features not mentioned.
